@OpenTelemetryTest_Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5042

### Get all products
GET {{OpenTelemetryTest_Api_HostAddress}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Get product by id
GET {{OpenTelemetryTest_Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a new product
POST {{OpenTelemetryTest_Api_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "New Product",
  "description": "A brand new product",
  "price": 49.99
}

### Update an existing product
PUT {{OpenTelemetryTest_Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "price": 59.99
}

### Delete a product
DELETE {{OpenTelemetryTest_Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Accept: application/json